<section id="about" class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-content animate-fade-in">
    <div class="profile-badge">Embedded & AI Engineer</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Integrating <span class="text-gradient">Hardware Signals</span><br/>
      with <span class="text-gradient">AI Intelligence</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      안녕하세요, <strong>이준영</strong>입니다.<br/>
      STM32 임베디드 제어부터 엣지 AI 모델 최적화까지,<br class="mo-break"/>
      <strong>데이터가 흐르는 모든 순간</strong>을 엔지니어링합니다.
    </p>
    
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn-primary">View Projects <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/junDevCodes" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a>
        <a href="mailto:jundevcodes@gmail.com"><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i></a>
        <a href="https://www.kaggle.com/ssafyseoul18ljy" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-kaggle"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-stats glass-panel animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-microchip"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-info">
        <span class="value">Embedded</span>
        <span class="label">STM32 / HAL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-info">
        <span class="value">AI Vision</span>
        <span class="label">Qwen / YOLO</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired"></i></div>
      <div class="stat-info">
        <span class="value">Backend</span>
        <span class="label">Django / Docker</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .profile-badge {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: var(--c-accent-light);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
  }
  .social-links a {
    width: 45px;
    height: 45px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .social-links a:hover {
    background: var(--c-slate-800);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  /* Hero Stats */
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 40px;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .stat-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--c-accent);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .stat-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .stat-info .value {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .stat-info .label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .mo-break { display: none; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .stat-divider { display: none; }
    .mo-break { display: block; }
  }
</style>
